### Create order to trigger status sequence background job
# @name CreateOrderForBgJobRequest
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [201]
## TEST-HAS-BODY
POST {{ApiBaseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
X-Background-Delay: 1000

{
    "customerId": "teapie-bgjob-cust",
    "customerName": "BgJob Test Customer",
    "customerEmail": "bgjob@example.com",
    "totalAmount": 150.00,
    "status": "pending"
}

###

### Poll order until status reaches 'completed' via background job sequence
# @name PollOrderStatusCompletedRequest
## RETRY-UNTIL-TEST-PASS: Status should be completed
## RETRY-MAX-ATTEMPTS: 20
## RETRY-BACKOFF-TYPE: Constant
## RETRY-MAX-DELAY: 00:00:02
GET {{ApiBaseUrl}}/orders/{{CreateOrderForBgJobRequest.response.body.$.id}}
Accept: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
